mg_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355090/extras/250cdfcb169f3d6ec597bcbf8b6e03a6.avif?t=1745914621\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355090/extras/feb10bebe5c2f429b5a1d66e8f792b24.poster.avif?t=1745914621\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355090/extras/feb10bebe5c2f429b5a1d66e8f792b24.webm?t=1745914621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1355090/extras/feb10bebe5c2f429b5a1d66e8f792b24.mp4?t=1745914621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>    • Admire your fleet of trains with the cinematic view mode.<br>    • Challenge yourself in bonus side missions. Explore arid deserts in search of oil supplies, or develop a rocket launch program.<br>    • Show off your most impressive railway setups with a photo mode that includes a variety of filters and visual options.<br>    • Invest in the growth of your cities, or use zeppelins to export goods for extra profit.",
